// DNS Tunneling - Potential Data Exfiltration
// Detects abnormally long DNS queries that may indicate DNS tunneling for data exfiltration
// MITRE ATT&CK: attack.exfiltration, attack.t1048.001, attack.command_and_control, attack.t1071.004
DnsEvents
| where TimeGenerated >= ago(1h)
| where (strlen(QueryName) >= 50) or ((QueryName endswith ".windows.com" or QueryName endswith ".microsoft.com" or QueryName endswith ".windowsupdate.com"))
| project TimeGenerated, Computer, Account, CommandLine, InitiatingProcessFileName, EventID
| sort by TimeGenerated desc